efault to Start.<br><br>- Title Style<br><br>- Single select dropdown<br>- Options are H2 and H3<br>- Default to H3<br><br>- Component Width<br><br>- Single select dropdown. <br>- Options are Read (672px), Pop (1024px), Plus (1600px)<br>- Default to Pop.<br><br>- Hide from In Page Navigation (Boolean) Default to False<br>- Text Overlay Vertical Alignment<br><br>- Single select dropdown.<br>- Options are Top, Middle, Bottom.<br>- Default to Bottom<br>- Instructions: “The text overlay is displayed over the image.”<br><br>- Text Overlay Horizontal Alignment<br><br>- Single select dropdown<br>- Options are Start, Center, End<br>- Default to Start<br><br>- Image Aspect Ratio<br><br>- Single select dropdown. <br>- Options are 4x1 (shortest), 2.4x1 (short), 16x9 (normal), 4x3 (tall), 1x1 (taller), 3x4 (tallest), Original<br>- Default to 16x9 (normal)<br><br>- Button Style<br><br>- Single select dropdown<br>- Options are Primary, Secondary, Transparent, Standard link, Emphasized Link<br>- Default to Primary.<br><br>- Button Alignment<br><br>- Single select dropdown.<br>- Options are Start, Center, End<br>- Default to End.<br><br>- Button Color<br><br>- Single select dropdown.<br>- Options are Blue and Orange, Theme Color<br>- Default to Blue<br><br>- Add Chevron To Button<br><br>- Boolean, default to False<br>- Note: This adds a chevron icon to the button to show open and closed states.<br><br>- Background Color<br><br>- Single select dropdown. <br>- Options are White and Light Gray.<br>- Default to White. <br><br>- Background Color Top Padding<br><br>- Single select dropdown<br>- Options are 0px, 8px, 16px, 32px, and 64px.<br>- Default value is 32px (UX Design question)<br><br>- Background Color Bottom Padding<br><br>- Single select dropdown<br>- Options are 0px, 8px, 16px, 32px, and 64px.<br>- Default value is 32px (UX Design question)<br><br>- Create/update view models as necessary. |

